creator: PlayFlock
descriptionHtml:
Indy Cat - game, made in a popular nowadays match-3 genre.
The point of the game is to help Indy Cat find his magic Ball of Fate!
Complete levels one by one, make combinations of gems & solve entertaining puzzles!
Indy Cat is a free-to-play game, but you can always get yourself such elements as bonus moves and lives, that can be purchased for real money to help you in game!
descriptionShort: Help this cute little kitten find the Ball Of Fate! Travel together with Indy!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
What's new?
* We have added new levels of the core story!
* And improved lots of previous levels.
* Lets celebrate the 5000th level event together! Note that levels 24 and 25 in the event are the same as 4999 and 5000 so everyone gets a chance to test their skill no matter the current level progress!
Leave your feedback! It is your opinion that helps us to improve the game.
